            { id: 'maternity', text: '<b>Protect maternity care:</b> targeted support can stop the spread of “maternity deserts” that endanger mothers and babies.' },
            { id: 'economic-anchor', text: '<b>Save the local economy:</b> because a hospital is often the top employer, keeping it open protects the whole community.' }
