          'Missile-defense co-production and new systems (such as the Iron Beam laser) and how far the U.S. fields them itself.',
          'How the Gaza and wider regional situation reshapes the politics of aid in both U.S. parties.',
          'Shifts in U.S. public opinion and intra-party splits over the amount and conditions of aid.'
